text: Danielle is a female given name. It is pronounced [ dan-yel ]. It is feminine of the name Daniel. Daniel is Hebrew for "God is my judge". Danielle is a strongly popular female name for certain countries. This name was ranked #443 on the US Popular Names in 2021. There are many variants for this name. Famous people by the name include Danielle Steel and Danielle Fishel. This name is currently being used on Atlantic tropical cyclones. == People == * Danielle Harris, American actress, voice actress, and film director * Danielle Campbell, American actress * Danielle Fishel, American actress ==References== Category:Given names
